Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.09,0:00:05.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.76,0:00:14.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早安～
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.20,0:00:35.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我開動了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.10,0:01:00.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沙英
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.50,0:01:03.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.08,0:01:15.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由乃親  出什麼事了？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.02,0:01:17.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起  小宮
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.58,0:01:19.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你先去學校吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.80,0:01:26.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出什麼事了？聽到好大的一下聲響
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.06,0:01:27.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要緊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.22,0:01:28.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沙英學姐  尋學姐
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.81,0:01:29.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.50,0:01:33.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這可真是大事故啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.10,0:01:37.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我貼  我貼
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.27,0:01:39.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我綁
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.13,0:01:43.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種意外就是會在心急的時候發生呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.90,0:01:47.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的  我是在冰箱下面看到了某黑色物
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.87,0:01:49.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然是我看錯了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.69,0:01:50.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但當時嚇了一跳
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.16,0:01:52.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也有過
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.60,0:01:54.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣差不多就行了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.34,0:01:56.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起  謝謝大家幫忙
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.82,0:02:00.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,時間
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.12,0:02:01.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.81,0:02:04.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還不必緊張
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.99,0:02:09.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快衝啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.32,0:03:50.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,趕上了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.90,0:03:54.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種時候就體現出住在學校正對面的好處了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.12,0:03:54.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.99,0:03:57.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說  這個週末準備怎麼過？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.59,0:03:58.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去哪兒玩玩嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.31,0:04:02.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上週因為要考試哪都沒去成呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.39,0:04:04.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乾脆去遊樂園之類的地方大玩一番吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.13,0:04:07.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想去地下賣場
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.03,0:04:10.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地下賣場？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.38,0:04:11.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要買什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.32,0:04:14.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼都不買
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.89,0:04:19.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在開始發期末考試成績
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.47,0:04:21.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,平均分是55分
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.17,0:04:23.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍微有點低呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.04,0:04:26.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,25分以下的人是要補考的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.38,0:04:30.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這次的英文語法試題很難的說
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.40,0:04:32.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我能達到平均線嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.33,0:04:34.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我英文語法很不擅長的…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.39,0:04:39.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs25}Grammar　　　　　　　　{\r}\N話說  語法到底是什麼意思來著
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.53,0:04:41.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs25}Gram  　{\r}\N是不是克的比較級
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.59,0:04:44.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Gram  grammar  glamourous
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.26,0:04:45.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Glamourous？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.94,0:04:52.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小宮  成績怎麼樣？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.49,0:04:55.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不算太好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.79,0:04:56.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有點害怕呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.65,0:05:13.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由乃親？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.56,0:05:18.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,期末考試在昨天就結束了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.76,0:05:20.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖說還有課要上
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.01,0:05:23.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但心情已經完全進入了春假模式
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.73,0:05:26.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼  這個週末要去哪裡逛逛呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.38,0:05:28.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就在這時  意想不到的事件發生了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.03,0:05:31.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,英文語法不及格  下星期補考
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.58,0:05:33.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪裡還有心情去玩樂呀
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.30,0:05:42.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就因為這個原因
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.25,0:05:45.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天由乃親的Ｘ看上去比平時要大上一號
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.82,0:05:49.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由乃  打起精神來
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.05,0:05:52.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  大家都會盡全力幫你的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.10,0:05:54.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝大家了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.95,0:05:59.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還留著去年的筆記  來幫你補習吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.56,0:06:01.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.72,0:06:03.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,午飯就交給我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.85,0:06:05.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做些好吃的給你送去
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.95,0:06:07.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感激不盡
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.55,0:06:12.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我就來為由乃親 製造遊樂園氣氛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.61,0:06:14.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小宮  那樣只會讓我難過
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.45,0:06:22.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼  我們開始吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.33,0:06:24.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是  請多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.84,0:06:28.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過  24分呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.24,0:06:32.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,25分以下是不及格  我正好被卡下來了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.59,0:06:35.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  這裡是不是批錯了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.46,0:06:36.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.74,0:06:38.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  的確拼錯了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.38,0:06:40.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該是22分呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,2月28日
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.33,0:06:47.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓我大吃一頓吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.50,0:06:47.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.27,0:06:51.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.35,0:06:52.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快進來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.39,0:06:54.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難得的休息天  真是抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.01,0:06:56.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別客氣別客氣
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.52,0:07:03.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,午飯來了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.24,0:07:04.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尋學姐萬歲
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.79,0:07:10.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,烏龍麵
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.08,0:07:14.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由乃親要用英文說出這些食材的名稱才能吃
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.39,0:07:15.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突然來這麼一手？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.59,0:07:18.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…Noodle對吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.83,0:07:22.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Soup  還有Chicken  還有…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.41,0:07:25.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,魚糕
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.17,0:07:27.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,魚糕是什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.69,0:07:28.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由乃親  加油！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.70,0:07:28.79,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（我開動了）
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.98,0:07:31.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我覺得語法考試裡是不會出現這種問題的喲
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.90,0:07:32.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絕對不會的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.71,0:07:36.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Fishcake
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.98,0:07:46.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.12,0:07:51.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在複習什麼呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.92,0:07:53.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,考試已經結束了說
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.57,0:07:54.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉野屋老師
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.01,0:07:57.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在複習英文語法  因為要補考
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.53,0:08:02.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,英文語法？老師的英語很棒的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.09,0:08:05.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不愧是Glamourous
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.92,0:08:09.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I Love You～～～
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.72,0:08:11.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厲害的日式英語發音
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.66,0:08:16.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,進展怎麼樣？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.19,0:08:18.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的  多虧大家幫忙了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.95,0:08:22.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說起來  為什麼英文語法考得那麼差呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.79,0:08:28.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為數學和英文同一天考  我光顧著複習數學了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.30,0:08:30.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.14,0:08:31.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那數學考得不錯囉？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.07,0:08:32.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.29,0:08:36.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卷子剛剛發下來了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.11,0:08:41.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紙飛機？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.06,0:08:42.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,考得不怎麼樣嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.28,0:08:54.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了  還有最後一題就全複習完畢了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.61,0:08:58.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多虧大家的幫忙  順利複習完了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.92,0:09:01.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天的補考  感覺能輕鬆過關
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.32,0:09:05.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,問題：請把下面的句子譯為英語
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.12,0:09:08.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你喝了這個飲料會感覺很不舒服的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.90,0:09:24.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,差不多要結束了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.87,0:09:26.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由乃她不要緊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.66,0:09:27.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要緊的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.34,0:09:34.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.61,0:09:39.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…哇…Student
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.00,0:09:40.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.37,0:09:48.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.74,0:09:49.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由乃
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.90,0:09:53.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,考得怎麼樣？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.19,0:09:57.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們看
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.52,0:10:01.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乖～乖～
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.05,0:10:06.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我貼  我貼  我貼貼貼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.87,0:10:14.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,100分好厲害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.91,0:10:17.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝  不過是補考啦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.47,0:10:19.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那也很厲害了  因為全答對了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.67,0:10:24.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了  晚飯做好啦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.12,0:10:25.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,準備享用吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.40,0:10:27.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.55,0:10:29.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由乃做了什麼料理？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.43,0:10:31.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吞湯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.43,0:10:31.25,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（Stew念錯了。）
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.86,0:10:34.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,燉湯！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.48,0:10:40.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Potato  carrot  onion  broccoli  chicken
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.55,0:10:42.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Flour  bulbar
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.55,0:10:45.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由乃  夠了  已經夠了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.65,0:10:45.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Go
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.65,0:10:46.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,四
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.65,0:10:47.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.65,0:10:48.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,二
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.65,0:10:49.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.73,0:10:59.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,12點過了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.19,0:11:02.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的呢  一聊就回想起了好多事情
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.32,0:11:05.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由乃親做的燉湯  超美味的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.29,0:11:06.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還會做的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.42,0:11:09.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但考試不想再掛紅燈了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.91,0:11:13.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遊樂園  下次再去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.82,0:11:14.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.10,0:11:33.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全都能收租金了哪～
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.43,0:11:47.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,房東  早安
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.34,0:11:49.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正在掃走廊啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.87,0:11:50.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真不賴真不賴
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.08,0:11:52.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天有什麼事啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.91,0:11:55.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,過來打掃空房間的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.27,0:11:57.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一年級的新生就快要入住了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.78,0:12:06.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請問…是和我們不同的一年級生…吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.10,0:12:07.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這樣哦  二年級生
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.64,0:12:13.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小宮小宮
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.97,0:12:14.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,起床了沒？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.66,0:12:17.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由乃親  發生什麼事了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.38,0:12:18.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽我說
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.36,0:12:21.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,空房間就快要搬進一年新生了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.98,0:12:23.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這可是大新聞啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.47,0:12:28.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尋學姐  大新聞
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.22,0:12:29.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽說暖陽莊就快住滿人了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.74,0:12:36.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽說暖陽莊就快沉入地下了…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.74,0:12:36.12,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（一詞多義，宮子太興奮導致尋理解錯誤。）
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.26,0:12:38.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在說什麼呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.49,0:12:46.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要搬進兩個一年級生嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.54,0:12:48.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,終於要住滿了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.72,0:12:51.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是這麼說啊  都時隔三年了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.83,0:12:54.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久違的滋潤的小日子就快回來了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.48,0:12:56.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將發泡酒升級成啤酒
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.48,0:12:56.42,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（發泡酒是一種使用輔料高達75%以上的帶有氣泡的酒類。\n其口感外觀與普通啤酒相似，但成本低，相比啤酒更便宜。）
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.52,0:12:58.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每天都能喝上喜歡的白薯燒酒
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.78,0:13:01.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就連平時捨不得喝的Dom Pérignon酒都有幸一嚐…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.78,0:13:01.99,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（Dom Pérignon是Mo?t et Chandon公司所生產的香檳的品牌。）
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.68,0:13:03.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.40,0:13:05.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果有空的話幫我一起打掃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.82,0:13:07.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請人的話會很貴呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.32,0:13:16.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好髒
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.31,0:13:19.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,房間沒人用的話居然能髒成這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.20,0:13:24.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一年級生啊  會是什麼樣的孩子們呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.08,0:13:28.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比如長得比我還高點的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.26,0:13:32.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我覺得這點是肯定不會錯的啦～
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.66,0:13:39.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看著空空如也的房間就想起了自己搬過來時的情形呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.51,0:13:42.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是呢  真令人懷念
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.57,0:13:46.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實在我第一次見到沙英的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.55,0:13:49.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,覺得有些難以相處呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.84,0:13:51.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沙英呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.74,0:13:53.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒…沒什麼特別的感受
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.69,0:13:56.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不可能一點感想都沒有吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.62,0:14:01.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒那可能吧～不可能的吧～說說呀
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.73,0:14:04.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像糖人點心似的的女孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.14,0:14:16.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您好～外賣來了～
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.32,0:14:18.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.17,0:14:21.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沙英  把樓上那倆孩子叫來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.33,0:14:22.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.46,0:14:27.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是房東叫來的外賣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.98,0:14:29.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算是幫忙打掃的謝禮了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.16,0:14:31.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,承蒙款待
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.12,0:14:33.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有烤豬排便當
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.10,0:14:35.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雞肉南蠻煮
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.48,0:14:36.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,燒汁肉排便當
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.77,0:14:38.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雜炒蔬菜便當以及
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.85,0:14:40.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,烤肉特別餐
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.23,0:14:43.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,選自己喜歡的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.48,0:14:44.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好～
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.67,0:14:51.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧  這就是挑剩下的了嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.70,0:14:59.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了對了  暖陽莊內的網線已經接好了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.97,0:15:02.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想上網的話和我說聲就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.82,0:15:03.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,網線？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.01,0:15:06.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  住103的孩子拜託我弄的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.84,0:15:09.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是有電腦的孩子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.96,0:15:12.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暖陽莊終於也要進行IT革命了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.00,0:15:16.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宮子  知道IT革命是什麼的縮寫嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.12,0:15:18.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,In～ternet！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.99,0:15:29.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老師老師
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.98,0:15:32.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有聽說暖陽莊的大新聞了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.86,0:15:35.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有兩個一年級生要入住了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.37,0:15:37.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這件事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.82,0:15:41.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老師我也很喜歡迎接新人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.34,0:15:44.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在正忙著做準備呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.65,0:15:45.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老師也…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.39,0:15:51.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老師  那是用來…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.73,0:15:55.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打掃完畢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.23,0:15:56.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.20,0:16:01.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請問…房東  一年級生哪一天搬過來呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.86,0:16:05.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兩個人都是後天下午過來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.42,0:16:09.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,後天…明天一天做點什麼好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.49,0:16:15.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,畫新生的想像畫像吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.31,0:16:16.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用來做什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.65,0:16:25.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,4月3日  『歡迎來到暖陽莊』
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.15,0:16:33.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由乃親  感到緊張嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.56,0:16:35.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  稍微有點
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.48,0:16:36.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是怎麼樣的女孩子呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.15,0:16:38.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能不能相處得好呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.24,0:16:44.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一年前由乃親來這裡時的情景還記得嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.37,0:16:44.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.96,0:16:52.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊  最緊張的還是一年級生她們呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.67,0:16:54.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要打起精神來才行
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.91,0:17:01.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一起洗了澡呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.71,0:17:03.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真令人懷念啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.47,0:17:05.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.44,0:17:08.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但才剛過9點吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.06,0:17:10.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會錯的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.23,0:17:17.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沙英學姐  快點快點
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.43,0:17:21.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  也不用特地去迎接她們的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.19,0:17:26.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀  各位是？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.43,0:17:28.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們好  今後請多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.15,0:17:30.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.70,0:17:38.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紙箱全部放在這裡可以嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.29,0:17:39.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒問題
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.00,0:17:43.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們的工作就到此為止了  就此拜別
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.46,0:17:44.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.00,0:17:45.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辛苦你們了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.42,0:17:52.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼快就弄好了  離那孩子來還有段時間呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.78,0:17:53.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.31,0:18:00.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  大家一起去吃飯吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.17,0:18:27.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.84,0:18:47.09,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（鴉雀無聲…）
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.50,0:19:10.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到得真早呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.17,0:19:13.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我先去打個招呼吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.46,0:19:32.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  誰都不在嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.71,0:19:47.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃得好飽啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.38,0:19:49.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真幸福～
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.28,0:19:53.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真沒想到突然就被拖去吃飯了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.25,0:19:56.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是有這樣開朗的父母不也不錯嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.27,0:20:00.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來的就是那對夫妻的孩子和搞IT革命的孩子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.20,0:20:01.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是怎麼樣的女孩子呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.29,0:20:05.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快點回去準備好茶水等她們吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.16,0:20:05.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.51,0:20:39.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天真是一團亂啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.77,0:20:43.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本想迎接她們的卻被她們迎接了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.03,0:20:51.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能好好相處就好了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.11,0:20:52.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乃莉和小薺
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.35,0:20:58.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們好  是暖陽莊的各位…對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.02,0:20:59.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.01,0:21:00.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然如此
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.94,0:21:01.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請…請問…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.37,0:21:06.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你已經到這裡了啊  代我們向你的父母問好
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.41,0:21:09.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛剛和他們一起吃了飯呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.48,0:21:10.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是承蒙款待了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.80,0:21:11.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為…為什麼呀？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.85,0:21:13.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,順水推舟地就…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.82,0:21:15.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎…你是？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.45,0:21:18.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我叫薺  剛搬到203室來的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.77,0:21:20.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那也是新生吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.30,0:21:21.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來有同齡人的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.00,0:21:24.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我叫做乃莉  住103室
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.85,0:21:28.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好  我是201室的由乃
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.61,0:21:30.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,202室的宮子
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.44,0:21:32.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由乃和宮子是二年級生
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.08,0:21:35.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們是三年級生  我叫沙英  住102室
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.98,0:21:37.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是尋  多多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.52,0:21:39.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.07,0:21:40.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.38,0:21:42.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在正巧要搬行李
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.28,0:21:44.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍微有些手忙腳亂
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.94,0:21:46.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請別在意
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.58,0:21:48.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等安定下來了來我家喝杯茶吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.20,0:21:50.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有空的話大家一起來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.31,0:21:51.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.22,0:21:53.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那等下就去您那裡拜訪
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.64,0:21:55.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…那我也一起…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.25,0:21:56.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  我等你們～
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.18,0:22:01.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在生活穩定之前如果有什麼需要的話儘管開口
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.01,0:22:02.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.71,0:22:03.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多謝了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.55,0:22:06.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今後就多關照了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.75,0:22:10.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,4月3日  『完』  待續
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.04,0:23:44.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,告訴你們暖陽莊的三個優勢吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.21,0:23:45.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一  離學校很近
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.65,0:23:47.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第二  光照良好
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.70,0:23:49.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住得舒適也是個優勢呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.00,0:23:51.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新來的兩位覺得如何呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.10,0:23:56.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然還不是很清楚  但和大家在一起很開心
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.29,0:23:59.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…那個…請多多關照
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.13,0:24:00.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下一話是
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.74,0:24:03.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,『4月6日～7日  YES  NO』
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.86,0:24:06.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,『7月19日  Olive』
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.84,0:24:08.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們在暖陽莊裡等著你
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.30,0:24:10.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定要來看哦
